<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Name"> Name </span></h5>
<p>Core Protocols
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="References.3F_Where_can_I_read_about_it"> References? Where can I read about it </span></h5>
<p>Book: Software for your head Jim and Michele Mc Carthy
</p><p><a href="http://www.mccarthyshow.com/" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.mccarthyshow.com/</a>
</p><p><br />
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_is_its_central_functionality.3F">  What is its central functionality? </span></h5>
<p>Create and maintain a team in a state of shared vision: 
</p>
<ul><li> connectedness
</li><li> alignment
</li><li> vision
</li><li> decision
</li><li> action
</li></ul>
<p>e.g.
</p>
<ul><li> Ask me
</li><li> Check in
</li><li> Perfection Game
</li></ul>
<p><br />
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_does_the_tool_help_me_do.3F"> What does the tool help me do? </span></h5>
<p>working in teams faster, having great results in team and great time working together
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_problem_can_it_help_me_solve.3F"> What problem can it help me solve? </span></h5>
<p>problems of teams facin complex tasks or projects
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_do_I_use_this_tool_and_not_another_one.3F"> Why do I use this tool and not another one? </span></h5>
<p>It is the most effective
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_is_my_world_worse_if_I_don.27t_use_it.3F">  Why is my world worse if I don't use it? </span></h5>
<p>Then the team are less effective because of head gap
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_does_it_help_solve_the_problem.3F">  Why does it help solve the problem? </span></h5>
<p>1) Because it relies on our natural need to connect and to help
2) it is formal and easy to learn
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="In_which_contexts_is_this_tool_useful.3F"> In which contexts is this tool useful? </span></h5>
<p>context of a team that decided to get greater results
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Who_can_benefit_from_using_this_tool.3F">  Who can benefit from using this tool? </span></h5>
<p>Any team, Teams of teams or company/organisation
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_abilities_do_people_need_to_have_to_be_able_to_benefit_from_this_tool.3F"> What abilities do people need to have to be able to benefit from this tool? </span></h5>
<p>open-mindedness, overcome the voice of judgement, fear or cynicism
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_are_the_main_benefits_of_using_this_tool.3F">  What are the main benefits of using this tool? </span></h5>
<p>team with shared vision creating great product/services
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Are_there_any_side-benefits_from_using_this_tool.3F"> Are there any side-benefits from using this tool? </span></h5>
<p>connecting oneself again with our personal greatness
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_are_the_downsides_of_using_this_product.3F"> What are the downsides of using this product? </span></h5>
<p>It is unusual and can frighten people
Its formality can repel non technical people
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Are_there_any_dangers.2Frisks_involved.3F">  Are there any dangers/risks involved? </span></h5>
<p>creating a gap between "booted" team and non booted teams
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="In_what_situations_would_this_tool_NOT_work_for_people.3F"> In what situations would this tool NOT work for people? </span></h5>
<p>no management buy in
no appropriate coaching for learing the tool
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Can_this_tool_be_overused.3F"> Can this tool be overused? </span></h5>
<p>Using it in every situation (non work related)
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Does_the_tool_really_solve_all_the_problem_or_are_there_aspects_not_solved.3F"> Does the tool really solve all the problem or are there aspects not solved? </span></h5>
<p>All teams working on a complex task can use the core protocols
</p><p><br />
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Are_there_any_tradeoffs.3F"> Are there any tradeoffs? </span></h5>
<p>people who just learned how to use the tool shouldn't assume others should conform to it
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Can_using_this_tool_cause_other_problems.3F"> Can using this tool cause other problems? </span></h5>
<p>depending on your environment
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Do_I_need_to_use_other_tools_in_order_to_get_the_full_benefit_from_this_tool.3F"> Do I need to use other tools in order to get the full benefit from this tool? </span></h5>
<p>no
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Other_Information"> Other Information </span></h5>
<p>There is work in progress to develop a less formal version of the core protocols
</p><p>Back to <a href="index.php?title=InterpersonalTools" title="InterpersonalTools">InterpersonalTools</a>
</p>
